ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 24th day of February, 2016, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
